aids.\n9 x 12 Axminsters\n$2.00 Down\n$5.00 Weekly\n(Small Carrying Charge)\nW e bought 5,000 rugs to get this price\nAH seamless. Firm weave. Deep pile.\nWill give years of service. All wool.\nBroadcloth Shirts\nChoose Now on\nLay Away Plan\nfor Christmas\n$1.04\nWell tailored shirts of PRE-SHRUNK\nfast color broadcloth. Full cut sizes.\nOcean shell buttons. Exceptional values!\nWindsor Gyrators\n$69.50\n(Small Carrying Charge)\nA fine efficient eiectric washer of out\nstanding beauty. Strong motor. No cen\nter posts. Genuine LoveH Wringer.\nFuH Fashioned\nWomen's Pure\nSilk Hose in\nNew Coiors\u2014\nFine sheer weave in a quality that seiis\nreguiariy for as high as $1.00. New curved\nFrench heei.\nMen s Work Shoes\nThey self\nreguiariy\nfor $2.98\n$2.14\nSelected quality brown leather uppers,\noak tanned weather-proof soles. Nailed and\nsewed construction.\nMONTGOME\nCo.\n24-26 E. 2nd. St.\nIncorp orated\nM AYSVtLLE, KY.\ni USE WARD'S CHR!STMAS LAY AWAY PLAN!","height":"29096","width":"21740"}}
